(3663, 1, '2017-06-26 11:24:01', '2017-06-26 02:24:01', 'Remon_screenshot_ 2\r\nPublish the Vietnamese version of the fantasy novel series \"Re: Monster\" (published by Alphapolis) on the web on a series of big hits and simultaneous announcement of delivery schedule of real name real-time RPG \"Re: Monster\" for smartphone Vietnamese version\r\n~ Fan event inviting authors held on Vietnam on Sunday, June 4 ~\r\n\r\nZodiac Asia Co., Ltd. (President Noriko Kato 2F - 2 - 6 in Roppongi, Minato-ku, Tokyo) acquired exclusive distribution right in Vietnamese of real real-time RPG \"Re: Monster\" from Alphapolis Corporation , Vietnamese version will be delivered from June 27 this year through Vietnamese corporation Fujitech JSC, a related subsidiary of Zodiac Asia. Entera Asia Co., Ltd. (7-10-18, Chuo-ku, Chuo-ku, Tokyo; Representative Director Masahiko Aoki) acquired Vietnamese translation rights of original novels from AlphaPolis Co., Ltd. and publishes it through local publishing company AMAK Media Publishing We have decided. To celebrate the distribution of the application and the publication decision of the translated book, on 4th June (Sun), we invited the original author Kim Kutsuko Fox (Kanekiru Tsuchine) to the city of Hanoi, Vietnam We will hold it.\r\n\r\n&lt;Outline of fan event holding&gt;\r\nDate and time: June 4, 2017 (Sunday) 2 pm - (Vietnam local time)\r\nLocation: Sakura Station 2F, Thang Long Number One Bldg Tower B, 1 Thang Long St., Tu Liem Dist., Hanoi, Vietnam\r\nContents: Introduction of the talk show, welcoming the original author Kim Kutsuko Fox (Guest), real real-time RPG \"Re: Monster\" and the Vietnamese novel\r\n&lt;Vietnamese version \"Re: Monster\" application overview&gt;\r\nBased on \"Re: Monster\" delivered to the world, it will be a Vietnamese version localized for Vietnamese players\r\nTitle (Vietnamese): Re: Monster-Hồi sinh thành quái vật\r\nGenre: Real time RPG\r\nPlatform: GooglePlay (Android) AppStore ((iOS)\r\nPrice: Free download (with partial item billing)\r\nScheduled delivery date: June 27, 2017\r\n(C) Kogitsune Kanekiru (C) AlphaPolis Co., Ltd.\r\n&lt;Original novel Vietnamese version overview&gt;\r\nWe plan to publish the Vietnamese version of \"Re: Monster\" 1 to 3 volumes from AMAK Media Publishing by local publisher around September 2017. &lt;Company profile&gt;\r\nCompany name: Zodiac Asia Ltd.\r\nLocation: 2 - 6 Roppongi Minato-ku, Tokyo Fukuyoshicho Building 6F\r\nRepresentative: Noriko Kato, Representative Director\r\nBusiness description: Established Fujitech JSC as a related subsidiary in Vietnam, develop offshore development business, mobile contents and game publishing business in Vietnam and Southeast Asian markets.\r\nURL: http://zodia-q.com/\r\nCompany name Zodiac Asia Ltd.\r\nLocation 2 - 6 Roppongi Minato-ku, Tokyo Fukuyoshi cho Building 6 F\r\nEstablishment February 8, 2013\r\nCapital 7,750,000 yen (including capital reserve)\r\nRepresentative Director Noriko Kato\r\nBusiness contents Offshore development business based on Vietnam, content publishing business, consulting and advancement support\r\nU R L http://www.zodia-q.com/\r\nRelated subsidiary Fuji Technology Co., Ltd. (Hanoi, Vietnam)\r\nCompany name Enterprise Asia Co., Ltd.\r\nLocation Ginza 7-10-18 Chuo-ku, Tokyo\r\nEstablishment February 8, 2013\r\nRepresentative Director Masahiko Aoki\r\nBusiness Description We operate the first Japanese TV channel \"View TV\" in Vietnam, and we also handle translation and publishing business of comic books and light novels. \"Sakura Station\" opened as a base station for originating Japanese brands in Hanoi\r\nU R L http://enterasia.jp/\r\nFor inquiries: Zodiac Asia Co., Ltd. Yasumasa Hibi (Hisa · Yasushi)\r\nE-mail address: hibi.yasumasa@fujitechjsc.com\r\nPhone number: Vietnam + 84 (0) 162 962 2061 / Japan + 81 (0) 90 1116 4573', 'Simultaneous announcement of Vietnamese version of fantasy novel \"Re: Monster\" issued and delivery of real real time RPG Vietnamese version for smartphone', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'simultaneous-announcement-vietnamese-version-fantasy-novel-re-monster-issued-delivery-real-real-time-rpg-vietnamese-version-smartphone', '', '', '2017-06-26 11:24:01', '2017-06-26 02:24:01', '', 0, 'http://zodiaq.lo/?p=3663', 0, 'post', '', 0),
