(3693, 1, '2017-06-26 16:41:58', '2017-06-26 07:41:58', '\n    <h2>About Us</h2>\n    <h5>Heading to our future</h5>\n    <h3>We embody muscular management that eliminates waste and aim for coexistence and prosperity with partners and customers.</h3>\n    <br>\n    <p>Since its establishment in February 2012, Zodiac Asia has challenged various projects mainly in Southeast Asia such as Vietnam and Thailand. Repeatedly failing and succeeding has become our bloodwork, and now we promise that we can make certain proposals to our partners and customers.</p>\n	<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VkTV9mLe7q0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n    <h2>Our projects</h2>\n    <h5>Introduction of our case studies</h5>\n    <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"\">\n        <img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://zodiaq.toilamit.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Remon_screenshot_2-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n    <h4><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Publishing game: The Cube\" rel=\"bookmark\">Publishing game: The Cube</a></h4>\n    <p>Description of project 1</p>\n    <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"\">\n        <img width=\"549\" height=\"308\" src=\"http://zodiaq.toilamit.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/q-club.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://zodiaq.toilamit.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/q-club.png 549w, http://zodiaq.toilamit.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/q-club-300x168.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\"> </a>\n    <h4><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"IT Outsourcing:「managiment for restaurants and shops」\" rel=\"bookmark\">IT Outsourcing:「managiment for restaurants and shops」</a></h4>\n    <p>Description of project 2</p>\n    <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"\">\n        <img width=\"300\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://zodiaq.toilamit.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Remon_screenshot_2-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n    <h4><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"Consulting: \" rel=\"